<br>
We did find the exit and got out.  The first thing we realized is that it is not doable by a 38 Shami and 39 SK alone.  We have both levelled again to 39 and 40.  <br>
<br>
Scratchy and I have been all the way to the top and killed everything this building can throw at you on another server (just never had to find the dang exits eheheh).  We know the way, what drops the key, loot etc.  <br>
<br>
This post is to see if there are any of you neutral-evil types out there that would like to adventure in this tower with us?  Some class types that would compliment us and make this a easy adventure are:<br>
<br>
Wiz or druid-nukage/DS/evac<br>
Mez<br>
Cleric/healer<br>
another mellee (sp 1 or two l's i cant remember eheh)<br>
<br>
Anyways post here and if we get some interest I will pick a date and time to meet and we will see how far we get into the Tower.  <br>
<br>
Up front I will ask that scratchy be allowed to loot keys as She plans to let the server know she has them for future rescue missions to save people who have unfortunate runins like we did Tuesday.  Any loot will be NB4G and rolled after that.  Also there are some nice quests that can be completed here if you have the faction so you may want to look them up.<br>
